    "description": "<strong>NOTICE: 由于此体验中使用了8K视频，AMD显卡不兼容。为此给您带来的不便我们深感抱歉。</strong><br><br>踏上进入Hottieverse的旅程，这是全球最具创新和高科技的音乐体验。您将置身于Megan Thee Stallion的私人演出现场，每一个音符和歌词都在令人惊叹的虚拟现实中得到放大。想象一下身处独家VIP音乐会，但又充满激动地潜入一个完全实现的数字世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269330/extras/fbd6ff80edc61a0e9590d70b6ed5ae27.poster.avif?t=1686169487\" width=624 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269330/extras/fbd6ff80edc61a0e9590d70b6ed5ae27.webm?t=1686169487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269330/extras/fbd6ff80edc61a0e9590d70b6ed5ae27.mp4?t=1686169487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>并非所有人都能进入。入口设有防护措施，防止闯入者的入侵。只有那些具备破解安全系统技能的人才能与Megan Thee Stallion面对面。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269330/extras/2b348c29b614cf7a9f66b46ea588ab7f.poster.avif?t=1686169487\" width=624 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269330/extras/2b348c29b614cf7a9f66b46ea588ab7f.webm?t=1686169487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269330/extras/2b348c29b614cf7a9f66b46ea588ab7f.mp4?t=1686169487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>舞台宏大无比。近距离体验她的现场表演会让音乐变得更加响亮、节奏更加强烈，充满激情。<br><br>不要错过这场史上最高质量的VR音乐会。踏入Megan Thee Stallion的世界，让音乐带您狂欢。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269330/extras/fd7d43fe5f39ed1039259a46c761fd61.poster.avif?t=1686169487\" width=624 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269330/extras/fd7d43fe5f39ed1039259a46c761fd61.webm?t=1686169487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269330/extras/fd7d43fe5f39ed1039259a46c761fd61.mp4?t=1686169487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>免费试用提供一个交互舞台的预览。完整的“Enter Thee Hottieverse” VR音乐会可以在应用中购买，包括幕后花絮和可分享的精彩片段。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269330/extras/30fd01c8bc1035c979a5c402b56280a2.poster.avif?t=1686169487\" width=624 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269330/extras/30fd01c8bc1035c979a5c402b56280a2.webm?t=1686169487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269330/extras/30fd01c8bc1035c979a5c402b56280a2.mp4?t=1686169487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Megan Thee Stallion是AmazeVR推出的众多艺术家中的首位。请期待今年夏天更多的VR音乐会。",
